HEADWORD: Planet-struck
<hw>Plan"et-struck`</hw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>a.</pos> <def>Affected by the influence of
planets; blasted.</def> <rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Like <qex>planet-stricken</qex> men of yore⟦br⟧
He trembles, smitten to the core⟦br⟧
By strong compunction and remorse.</q>
<rj><qau>Wordsworth.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Planetule</ent>⟦br⟧
